【柴犬春卷】🦊我是2019年10月15日出世的小朋友，出世兩個月就去了春爸和春媽的家，我的名字叫｢春卷｣，今年兩歲了，最喜歡吃零食和睡覺。

2021年8月25日我們來到英國展開新生活，每一天都過得很愉快，自由自在的與爸爸媽媽繼續探索新事物。

___________________________________ 
【Shiba Harumaki】I am a kid who was born on 15 October 2019.  I went to the homes of Chun Dad and Chun Mom two months after birth.  My name is "Harumaki".  I am two years old now.  I like snacks and sleeping. 

We came to the UK to start a new life on 25 August 2021.  We had a great time every day and we will continued to explore new things.🥰
